title: Greater Quintessences Of Movement Speed not showing?
body: Hi, I noticed while changing my runes around that I only have 2 Greater Quintessences Of Movement Speed when I purchased the 3rd one I needed in December. I even checked to see in the purchase history and it is listed that I did. Please help me c: thank you

replies.body: I guess i'll just buy it again and not leave the legacy client. no biggy
It didn't work. I still only have 2 in the list.

I've seen some players encounter issues seeing certain runes after removing them from certain rune pages. You should be able to resolve this by swapping over to the Legacy Client to edit your rune pages. Afterward, you should see the runes again in the Beta Client.

Please hit me back if this worked.

my scaling ad runes on my other account aren't showing either
